item.title: Friday night
item.dc:creator: troyh
item.content:encoded: We worked on the new Talk until 7 or so and then went to Bishop's for dinner. We came home, watched some TiVo and went to bed. Got up early (6am) thanks to the dogs and my pager going off (MySQL connections maxed out). Need to finish the new Talk stuff and get it up tonight. I'd like to relax tomorrow.
